title: 'Throw away deal. Simply go for it'
body: 'Cozy and comfortable. Good fit. Worthy deal for the price. Product matched exactly as shown. Used it in minus 3 degrees in Uttarakhand. This alone will not protect you from cold. Need good thermals or sweater inside. This serves as a good overcoat types. Good for maybe 10 degrees or so. I bought 3 colors. Looking at this my friend got 4 pieces (at a further reduced price each)'

title: 'Quality product'

title: 'A good buy for home use'
body: This is a good sweatshirt for wearing at home during winters. The price is fluctuating a lot. I bought it for 649/- and in two days the price dropped to 559/-. So, yeah you can wait and get a good deal if it's not urgent. I saw the red one selling for 449/-.  It is warm and good for cities where temps go as low as 10 degrees Celsius. For colder areas you might want to wear additional layers of clothing.  The sweatshirt didn't loose its quality after washing. So no worries in that department.

title: 'Worth the money'
